                                                          Dear Daniel,
                                                          dear Andrew,<br>
                                                          <br>
                                                          Thank you for
                                                          your e-mail
                                                          and the data.<br>
                                                          Concerning
                                                          geometry
                                                          differences:
                                                          these are very
                                                          small and come
                                                          from the fact
                                                          that Anita
                                                          used Gaussian
                                                          and Turbomole
                                                          to verify the
                                                          consistency of
                                                          the results.
                                                          She sent you
                                                          the Gaussian
                                                          optimized
                                                          geometries but
                                                          then followed
                                                          up with
                                                          Turbomole
                                                          calculations.
                                                          Finally, we
                                                          decided to
                                                          base all
                                                          results on
                                                          Turbomole and
                                                          she changed
                                                          the
                                                          coordinates in
                                                          the Supp. Mat.
                                                          I am attaching
                                                          her comments.
                                                          You can see
                                                          there that
                                                          differences
                                                          are negligible
                                                          and you need
                                                          not redo the
                                                          calculations.<br>
                                                          Concerning the
                                                          question of
                                                          the symmetry
                                                          in the UDFT
                                                          geometry
                                                          optimizations
                                                          for structures
                                                          4-8. These
                                                          were performed
                                                          for the
                                                          singlet ground
                                                          states. The
                                                          closed shell
                                                          high-symmetry
                                                          DFT solution
                                                          is unstable.
                                                          The spin
                                                          unrestricted
                                                          (U)DFT
                                                          wavefunction
                                                          is symmetry
                                                          broken and has
                                                          only Cs
                                                          symmetry. You
                                                          can see the
                                                          orbitals=C2=A0 in
                                                          Figs. 9S-13S
                                                          of the Supp.
                                                          Mat. The C2h
                                                          in Fig. 10S
                                                          should also
                                                          read as Cs.
                                                          Thus, the MOs
                                                          have Cs
                                                          symmetry, but
                                                          alpha and beta
                                                          orbitals are
                                                          equivalent so
                                                          that the
                                                          structural
                                                          symmetry is
                                                          higher, C2h
                                                          and D2h,
                                                          respectively.
                                                          Thus, the
                                                          formulations
                                                          should be
                                                          correct.
                                                          However, we
                                                          will explain
                                                          this in the
                                                          text. See also
                                                          Anita&#39;s
                                                          comments
                                                          attached.<br>
                                                          I am also
                                                          attaching a
                                                          paper on
                                                          oligoacenes
                                                          where you see
                                                          the same
                                                          effect, the
                                                          symmetry
                                                          broken
                                                          orbitals
                                                          (Figure 2) and
                                                          the higher
                                                          symmetry of
                                                          the geometry.<br>
                                                          <br>
                                                          Do you agree?<br>
                                                          <br>
                                                          Please see my
                                                          follow-up
                                                          e-mail on the
                                                          symmetry
                                                          breaking.<br>
